{"tid":2332477,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"（有卡！）施永青提「聖誕」：X你老母","createTime":"2020-12-19T15:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T16:01:34.000Z","uid":54870,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"87f5ef6ffddcb0b28897a4437a61254635a19714","tid":2332477,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T15:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Djzhibv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDjzhibv.jpg&h=2835702d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（張野改自其他巴打作品，希望唔好介意）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過中原地產創辦人施永青對「聖誕」就有HardFeeling，《壹週刊》報道，施永青一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「我最憎就是聖誕！」，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n依家施永青財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！"},{"pid":"ec38dad3c58bf1270dfa9a36b30a5a876154e542","tid":2332477,"uid":108545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T15:52:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d20587f6a326d38bde07badf13c2f1e516bb797","tid":2332477,"uid":54870,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T15:52:38.000Z","msg":"大家不妨學下永青<br />\n循環再用聖誕卡<br />\n同施生分享聖誕嘅喜悅"},{"pid":"f705ad656ee7d6466db0b23f35f84f30f8f29780","tid":2332477,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0d20587f6a326d38bde07badf13c2f1e516bb797","tid":2332477,"uid":54870,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T15:52:38.000Z","msg":"大家不妨學下永青<br />\n循環再用聖誕卡<br />\n同施生分享聖誕嘅喜悅"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T15:55:04.000Z","msg":"好  寄去佢公司"},{"pid":"9eba1a93b3e9cdd1dcc91bf89804e86b76aebb1f","tid":2332477,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T16:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9mX0eDZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t